## Step 2: Add sheet CRUD actions to SketchProvider

**File:** `src/modules/sketch/app/SketchProvider.jsx`

Add 6 reducer actions (same pattern as `ProjectProvider.jsx` lines 547-606):
- `SKETCH_SHEET_ADD` ‚Äî push sheet to `state.project.sheets`
- `SKETCH_SHEET_UPDATE` ‚Äî merge updates for matching sheet id
- `SKETCH_SHEET_DELETE` ‚Äî filter out by id
- `SKETCH_SHEET_VIEWPORT_ADD` ‚Äî find sheet, append viewport to its `viewports[]`
- `SKETCH_SHEET_VIEWPORT_UPDATE` ‚Äî find sheet, update matching viewport
- `SKETCH_SHEET_VIEWPORT_DELETE` ‚Äî find sheet, filter out viewport

All wrapped with `applyUpdate(state, ...)` for undo/redo history.

