## Step 9: Create sheet template generators

**New file:** `src/modules/sketch/sheets/sketchSheetTemplates.js`

- `generateAssemblySheet(project, assemblyId)` ‚Äî creates a sheet with 3 assembly view viewports (top/front/side) + a part list viewport. Sets `sourceRefId: assemblyId`, title from assembly name, scale computed from assembly bounds (target ~1:5 for furniture).

- `generatePartDetailSheet(project, partId)` ‚Äî creates a sheet with 1 part detail viewport. Sets `sourceRefId: partId`, title from part name, scale computed from part extents.

Both use `createSheet()` and `createSheetViewport()` from `@/domain/sheetModels`.

